---
---
<section id="about">
  <div class="grid">
    <div class="photo-col" data-reveal>
      <div class="photo-frame">
        <img src="/assets/headshot.jpg" alt="Frida H.K." />
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="text-col" data-reveal style="transition-delay: 0.1s">
      <p class="eyebrow">About</p>
      <h2>The reader your book deserves before anyone else meets it</h2>
      <p>
        I'm Frida — an editor who has spent the better part of a decade in the quiet company of
        other people's sentences. I came to this work the long way, through bookshops and slush
        piles and far too many late nights with a red pencil, and I've never quite gotten over the
        thrill of helping a story find its truest shape.
      </p>
      <p>
        Every manuscript that lands on my desk gets the same thing: unhurried attention, an honest
        ear, and a deep respect for the voice that's already there. I'm not here to make your book
        sound like mine — I'm here to make it sound unmistakably, confidently like you.
      </p>
      <p class="signature">— Frida H.K.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  section {
    max-width: 1120px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: clamp(60px, 9vw, 110px) 32px;
  }

  .grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
    gap: clamp(40px, 6vw, 80px);
    align-items: center;
  }

  /* Photo */
  .photo-frame {
    position: relative;
    aspect-ratio: 4 / 5;
    border: 1px solid rgba(155, 163, 145, 0.5);
    border-radius: 3px;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .photo-frame img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
    object-position: center top;
    display: block;
  }

  /* Text */
  .eyebrow {
    font-family: var(--font-ui);
    font-size: 12.5px;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.24em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--accent);
    margin-bottom: 22px;
  }

  h2 {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: clamp(32px, 4.6vw, 48px);
    line-height: 1.12;
    color: var(--ink);
    margin-bottom: 28px;
  }

  p {
    color: var(--muted);
    font-size: 18px;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }

  .signature {
    margin-top: 32px;
    margin-bottom: 0;
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-style: italic;
    font-size: 26px;
    color: var(--ink);
  }
</style>
